    dc:title "Taxonomic review of the grassland leafhopper genus Maiestas Distant (Hemiptera: Cicadellidae: Deltocephalinae: Deltocephalini) from Pakistan with description of a new species and two new records" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5635914>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5635918>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5635920>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5635932>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5635924>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5635930>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5635926> ;
