<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5635914>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Maiestas species.A–D, M. albomaculata (Dash & Viraktamath) (after Naveed et al., 2019) A: habitus, dorsal view; B: face; C: connective and aedeagus, dorsal view; D: connective and aedeagus, lateral view; E, M. indica (Singh-Pruthi) (after Dash & Viraktamath, 1998): connective and aedeagus, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5635914/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5635918>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Maiestas maculata (Singh-Pruthi). A: habitus, dorsal view; B: habitus, lateral view; C: head and thorax, dorsal view; D: face; E: male genital capsule, lateral view; F: subgenital plate, valve and style, dorsal view; G: connective, dorsal view (detached from aedeagus); H: aedeagus, dorsal view; I: aedeagus, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5635918/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5635920>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Maiestas sinuata Shah & Duan sp. n. A: habitus, dorsal view; B: habitus, lateral view; C: head and thorax, dorsal view; D: face; E: male genital capsule, lateral view; F: subgenital plates, valve and styles, dorsal view; G–H: connective and aedeagus, dorsal and lateral view respectively." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5635920/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5635932>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Maiestas sp. 1. A: habitus, dorsal view; B: habitus, lateral view; C: head and thorax, dorsal view; D: face; E: subgenital plates, valve, styles, connective and aedeagus, dorsal view; F: aedeagus, dorsal view; G: connective and aedeagus, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5635932/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5635924>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Maiestas species. A–E, M. subviridis (Metcalf) (after Khatri & Webb, 2010) A–B: habitus (macropterus and subbrachypterus respectively), dorsal view; C: subgenital plate, ventral view; D: aedeagus, lateral view; E: aedeagus, dorsal view; F–L, M. pruthii (Metcalf) (after Dash & Viraktamath, 1998) F: habitus, dorsal view; G: habitus, lateral view; H: face; I: style, dorsal view; J: connective and aedeagus, ventral view; K; apex of aedeagus, lateral view; L: connective and aedeagus, lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5635924/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5635930>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Maiestas trispinosa (Dash & Viraktamath). A: habitus, dorsal view; B: habitus, lateral view; C: head and thorax, dorsal view; D: face; E: male genital capsule, lateral view; F: subgenital plates, valve and styles, dorsal view; G: connective and aedeagus, dorsal view; H–I: connective and aedeagus, ventral and lateral view respectively." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5635930/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5635926>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Maiestas tareni (Dash & Viraktamath). A–H: this study, A: habitus, dorsal view; B: habitus, lateral view; C: head and thorax, dorsal view; D: face; E: male genital capsule, lateral view; F: subgenital plate, valve and styles, dorsal view; G & H: connective and aedeagus, dorsal and lateral view; I–N: after Zhang & Duan, 2011, I: habitus, dorsal view; J: male pygofer lobe, lateral view; K: subgenital plate, ventral view; L: style, dorsal view; M & N: connective and aedeagus, dorsal and lateral view; O–T: after Khatri & Webb, 2010, O: habitus, dorsal view; P: head and thorax, dorsal view; Q: subgenital plate, ventral view; R: style, dorsal view; S & T: connective and aedeagus, dorsal and lateral view; U–Z: after Dash & Viraktamath, 1995, U: head and thorax, dorsal view; V: face; W: subgenital plates and valve, dorsal view; X: style, dorsal view; Y & Z: connective and aedeagus, dorsal and lateral view respectively." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5635926/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

